node.title: Police appeal for help to locate murder suspect
node.description: West Auckland police are asking for public help to find a suspect in a homicide investigation.
node.content:
["West Auckland police are asking for public help to find a suspect in a homicide investigation.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "Three people have been charged with murder after Robert James Hart died in New Lynn last Friday.", "The police have now gone public in their attempt to find another suspect, Dylan James Mitchell Harris.", "The 35-year-old, who has gang connections across the North Island, has a warrant for arrest for murder.", "He's about 182cm tall, of medium build, and has a full sleeve tattoo on his left arm.", "He is considered dangerous and should not be approached."]
